    <text id="A9628T">
        <front id="d2">
            <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
                <p>John's letter to Kate contains news of family members and his thoughts on recent
                    troop movements in the Valley.</p>
            </div1>
        </front>

        <body id="d4">
            <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        <date value="1862-04-22">April 22 /62</date>
                        <name type="place">Camp in <unclear>Luiptrum</unclear> Gap</name>
                    </dateline>
                    <salute>Dear Sister</salute>
                </opener>

                <p>I am well &amp; <orig reg="have">hav</orig> been so for some time as Jacob
                    has given you a <orig reg="description">discription</orig> of our moves I will
                    not attempt it our friends &amp; relations in the army are all well. I
                    stayed all night with Aunt Lou on last Thursday night they are all well Uncle
                    Cyrus Rhodes buried his son Dalas week before last Mary &amp;
                    <unclear>Joce</unclear> are very <orig reg="poorly">porly</orig> they had the
                    diphtheria the rest of the relations are all well.</p>

                <p>I thought when we <orig reg="started">stared</orig> towards the Blue ridge that
                    we were going to give up the valley to them <del rend="none" hand="h1"/> us off from home
                    this made me feel very sorry but I am glad that we can hear from home yet I hope
                    that God is on our side &amp; will do all of the best my love to you all I
                    hope it will not be long <orig reg="until">untill</orig> we will see home and
                    may God bless you all</p>

                <closer>
                    <salute><orig reg="your">youre</orig> brother</salute>
                    <signed>John Armentrout</signed>
                </closer>
            </div1>
        </body>
    </text>
